title: Grateful Dead Live at Cal Expo on 1990-06-10
lineage: DAT Master > Sony PCM r500 > Tascam DA-3000 > Flac 16/48
description:
Set 1

Bertha, Jack Straw, Dire Wolf, Wang Dang Doodle, Row Jimmy, Picasso Moon, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Box Of Rain, Eyes Of The World-> Playin' In The Band-> Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> Gimme Some Lovin'-> Standing On the Moon-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: The Last Time

Phil announces that rumors of him leaving the band "are a bullshit lie"
